Bon VS mauvais (masc) / le mauvais temps - bad weather
Mauvaise / la mauvaise direction 

Le verbe "Avoir" - to have

J'ai - I have
Tu as - You have (informal)
Il,elle,on a - he,she,we(it - general) has

(Nous) av(ons) - we have
(Vous) (avez) - you have (formal)
Ils(m), elles(f) ont - they have

